OL,3,C'Real possibility' jailed PC was
OL,4,Cvictim of miscarriage of justice
OL,6,FA police officer who was jailed for
OL,7,Fassaulting a suspect could have his
OL,8,Fconvictions quashed by the Court of
OL,9,FAppeal.
OL,11,FDanny Major was sentenced to 15 months
OL,12,Fin jail after being found guilty at a
OL,13,Fretrial of battery and assault causing
OL,14,Factual bodily harm in 2006.
OL,16,FBut the Criminal Cases Review
OL,17,FCommission (CCRC) said evidence that
OL,18,Fwas not available at trial "raises a
OL,19,Freal possibility the Court of Appeal
OL,20,Fwill now quash those convictions".
