OL,3,C'Real possibility' jailed PC was
OL,4,Cvictim of miscarriage of justice
OL,6,FSubsequent challenges at the Court of
OL,7,FAppeal and with the Criminal Cases
OL,8,FReview Commission (CCRC) were
OL,9,Fdismissed.
OL,11,FIn 2013, Greater Manchester Police
OL,12,F(GMP) began an independent review of
OL,13,Fthe case, which concluded there was
OL,14,Ffresh evidence which cast doubt on his
OL,15,Fconviction.
