OL,3,C'Real possibility' jailed PC was
OL,4,Cvictim of miscarriage of justice
OL,6,FIts subsequent report was heavily
OL,7,Fcritical of the investigation carried
OL,8,Fout by West Yorkshire Police's
OL,9,Fprofessional standards department
OL,10,Fwhich resulted in Mr Major's
OL,11,Fconviction.
OL,13,FIn 2016 GMP launched a criminal
OL,14,Finvestigation into an alleged
OL,15,Fconspiracy to pervert the course of
OL,16,Fjustice by officers at West Yorkshire
OL,17,FPolice.
OL,19,FIn February 2020, the CCRC restarted
OL,20,Fits own review of the case.
